道</a></ins><ins><a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://deadline.com/2023/06/roland-emmerich-unveils-space-nation-franchise-tv-series-game-1235424714/"><em>最后期限</em></a></ins><ins><a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://deadline.com/2023/06/roland-emmerich-unveils-space-nation-franchise-tv-series-game-1235424714/">。</a></ins>如果您想了解开发进展情况，甚至还可以观看视频。 </p><div id="44528a78952c4f5294a6e75c88e4b7b1"><iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Fvu_sxa7RdU" title="YouTube 视频播放器" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p> <em>《Space Nation Online》</em>将让玩家踏上“揭开 Telikos 星团之谜的史诗之旅”，将于今年夏天晚些时候发布 alpha 版本，计划于 2024 年全面发布。假设取得一定程度的成功，动画短片、电视节目和衍生游戏随后出现。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/film-director-roland-emmerich-is-creating-a-shared-universe-of-tv-gaming-and-web3-tomfoolery-180028686.html ?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/film-director-roland-emmerich-is-creating-a-shared-universe-of-tv-gaming-and-web3-tomfoolery-180028686.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 6dc66220-552f-4de1-84e0-dacc332364d2</guid><dc:creator>劳伦斯·邦克</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 28 Jun 2023 18:00:28 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1687972779</ingested><modified> 2023-06-28T17:19:43+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Lawrence Bonk]]></category><media:content height="1200" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/199449b0-15d5-11ee-ad97-1ea2d7a59dc2" width="2002"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]><